{"tid":310432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無煙民成功戒煙 入黎分享下","createTime":"2017-07-05T20:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T07:29:45.000Z","uid":74028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0371b6f4b3335ec20f05aed3bb3c174d473c7c41","tid":310432,"uid":74028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T20:41:07.000Z","msg":"食左四年煙，六日前因為啲事入左醫院訓左晚加上又突然無乜意欲食煙，出院個陣索性試下戒埋佢，點知頭兩日都好地地，第三晚開始訓唔到教，一到夜晚就好似感冒咁，全身發熱出哂汗，每個夜晚都會偏頭痛，痛到訓唔到。<br />\n開頭以為普通感冒，去左睇醫生，有keep住食感冒藥，但岩岩又痛醒開始諗，關唔關戒煙事（明明無煙引），上網查睇到話戒煙真係會訓唔着 頭痛等，半個鐘前試下食左支，點知食個陣同食完後真係無咁頭痛。<br />\n想各位師兄分享下戒煙心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我知食煙既人唔抵可憐，但我真心想戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3962d38aaa947837e0ff81901b64ade932ac08d0","tid":310432,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T20:43:02.000Z","msg":"一句話唔食就成功<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n煙齡半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50e8039422dee8e95e923a512b7307334e3c2d9","tid":310432,"uid":74028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T20:47:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一句話唔食就成功<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n煙齡半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想一句話戒就戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5027d4b8d1512b8384ed820f1a3a234ce8997348","tid":310432,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T20:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一句話唔食就成功<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n煙齡半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想一句話戒就戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個人覺得心癮大於身癮<br />\n我食個陣都話自己渡過當時難關就戒<br />\n其實當時解決左之後都已經唔想食<br />\nBtw 我煙齡太短 等其他巴絲講多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a2ef002fd90c77f618704bb2dbe73b454895cc","tid":310432,"uid":74028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T20:52:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一句話唔食就成功<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n煙齡半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想一句話戒就戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個人覺得心癮大於身癮<br />\n我食個陣都話自己渡過當時難關就戒<br />\n其實當時解決左之後都已經唔想食<br />\nBtw 我煙齡太短 等其他巴絲講多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我反而調轉 唔食個頭真係痛到仆街 病足咁多日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3ef2f694946d739efec2c3041c286fd3547a25","tid":310432,"uid":57643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T20:53:53.000Z","msg":"做運動啦"},{"pid":"1503fc46cfd8b26c1637fe1de487223c74f299ea","tid":310432,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T20:54:09.000Z","msg":"試下戒煙貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n博愛有免費針灸戈戒煙 等你少d退癮症狀 <br />\n<br />\n準備戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但身邊有人食就忍唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b30b3a075e3314dd281042c4026b8cfccb2b7e5","tid":310432,"uid":74028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T20:55:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做運動啦</blockquote><br />\n真係有用？我係一到夜晚keep住頭痛痛醒"},{"pid":"b5472d92633162e361276e7c8b775ab91e0e3c40","tid":310432,"uid":74028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T20:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下戒煙貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n博愛有免費針灸戈戒煙 等你少d退癮症狀 <br />\n<br />\n準備戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但身邊有人食就忍唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n半個鐘前破戒食左半支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />矛盾位係食完真係唔頭痛"},{"pid":"7a8c10b3caacb84ff3e58a5885b537ab723d2b14","tid":310432,"uid":104088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T23:05:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"330477c78f1acaa7c38a91b50e73c870273eb3a0","tid":310432,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T23:25:37.000Z","msg":"頭暈成身乏力就會， 頭痛真係未試過<br />\n只要你夠意志力頂一個星期就得<br />\n利申：食廿年煙已戒"},{"pid":"70b74e04f5dca07bdecf4b8c663d07e3906a51ee","tid":310432,"uid":66684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T23:35:02.000Z","msg":"食左六年  一話戒就一支都無食 開頭難頂啲 因為之前番工眼訓就成日去食煙 一開始戒就成日都好眼訓<br />\n到而家戒左個幾月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff1f453e408a8e7b50f392beb867e483d21e145","tid":310432,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:29:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}